            <h1>Clinical guidance for neonatal jaundice management</h1>
            <p class="hero-lead">A practical reference based on <strong>AAP 2022</strong> and <strong>NICE CG98</strong>, focused on phototherapy decisions, escalation of care, exchange transfusion, IVIG, and post-treatment monitoring.</p>
